{"tid":2326863,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"砌機求救！","createTime":"2020-12-15T15:29:20.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-16T03:53:54.000Z","uid":169162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"53b20d5f2f47191205575777f1cdbde77c53cfe2","tid":2326863,"uid":169162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今日砌咗部機<br />\n<br />\n通電試著嘅時候發現一時開到一時開唔到，應該點解決<br />\n<br />\n再細節啲試就係一插電制即刻開機就開到，插咗電制一段時間先開就開唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\nMotherboard: TUF gaming B450M-PRO S<br />\n顯示咭：GIGABYTE 3060ti <br />\nBE QUIET PURE LOOP 240mm水冷<br />\nAMD Ryzen 5 3600<br />\n2條GAMMIX D10 ram<br />\n牛： seasonic focus Gx-650 (80 plus gold) <br />\n<br />\n試過重新插過啲嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但都係要啱啱通電嗰下先開到機<br />\n<br />\n有冇巴打可以救我<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46890f651e89099d1051bf9a4e6531930adf597","tid":2326863,"uid":59691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T15:51:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.asus.com/tw/Motherboards/TUF-GAMING-B450M-PRO-S/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.asus.com%2Ftw%2FMotherboards%2FTUF-GAMING-B450M-PRO-S%2F&d=ZAqn3h4t0e4XfOyVRCtvGJriIWEbfV0cuvPRs67P9cA%3D&h=3d3ac5b4\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.asus.com/tw/Motherboards/TUF-GAMING-B450M-PRO-S/</a><br />\n底板BIOS FlashBack button 後面到攝張紙仔隔開機箱試下"},{"pid":"54b87f5a1b1fd5e154b6b1cb805a777c9d449635","tid":2326863,"uid":220942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-15T16:11:11.000Z","msg":"又純文字討論<br />\n淨睇字都幫你唔到啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosa